---
// omega-detail.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="The Omega Detail Process | 3-Day Car Restoration System"
  description="At Omega Detailing, we do not 'clean cars.' Explore our structured 3-day restoration system: preparation, paint correction, and 5-year ceramic coating."
>
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="bg-white pt-40 md:pt-48 pb-32 text-neutral-900 min-h-screen font-sans overflow-x-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20">
      
      {/* Title / Header */}
      <div class="mb-24 animate-fade-in">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-tight">
          OUR <span class="text-blue-600">PROCESS</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-2 bg-blue-600 mb-12"></div>
      </div>

      {/* Philosophy Section */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mb-36 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-neutral-950">
            An Entire System Dedicated to Restoration
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-700 font-medium leading-relaxed">
            At Omega Detailing, we do not “clean cars.” We follow a structured system of restoration—one that is deliberate, methodical, and rooted in the philosophy that a vehicle is never simply improved, but carefully brought back to its highest possible form.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
            Every car tells a story through its condition. Swirls, fading gloss, embedded contamination, and worn interiors are not just imperfections—they are layers of time. Our process exists to remove those layers with precision, discipline, and respect for the vehicle itself.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-r-2xl shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-extrabold text-neutral-950 leading-snug">
            This is not a quick service. It is a <span class="text-blue-600">3-day transformation system</span>, where each stage is given the time, attention, and control it demands.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Day-by-Day Stack */}
      <div class="space-y-32 mb-36">
        
        {/* Day 1 Section */}
        <div class="pt-20 border-t-2 border-neutral-100 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start group animate-slide-up">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-4 lg:sticky lg:top-48">
            <div class="text-xs font-black text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-2">Stage 01</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-neutral-950 leading-tight group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              Day 1: <br class="hidden lg:block" />Preparation & <br class="hidden lg:block" />Deep Decontamination
            </h2>
            <div class="w-12 h-1.5 bg-blue-600/30 group-hover:w-24 transition-all duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-800 font-extrabold leading-relaxed">
              The foundation of perfection is purity. Nothing meaningful can be corrected until the surface is completely reset.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
              On the first day, the entire focus is the removal of every form of dirt, contamination, and residue—both visible and hidden.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">This includes</h3>
              <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">A safe, structured exterior wash process</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Intensive wheel and brake dust removal</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Chemical decontamination to dissolve embedded iron particles and tar</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Clay bar treatment to remove bonded surface contamination</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Full interior deep cleaning, including seats, carpets, plastics, and hidden areas</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Extraction of dirt trapped within fibres, seams, and hard-to-reach surfaces</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed font-bold border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6 py-2">
              By the end of this stage, the vehicle is not yet perfected—but it is pure. Ready. Neutral. A blank canvas with no interference between paint and correction.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Day 2 Section */}
        <div class="pt-20 border-t-2 border-neutral-100 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start group">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-4 lg:sticky lg:top-48">
            <div class="text-xs font-black text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-2">Stage 02</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-neutral-950 leading-tight group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              Day 2: <br class="hidden lg:block" />Paint Correction <br class="hidden lg:block" />& Refinement
            </h2>
            <div class="w-12 h-1.5 bg-blue-600/30 group-hover:w-24 transition-all duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-800 font-extrabold leading-relaxed">
              True transformation begins when light interacts with a flawless surface.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
              Day two is dedicated entirely to paint correction—one of the most precise and skilled stages of the entire process.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
              Using machine polishing techniques, the paintwork is refined panel by panel to remove imperfections such as swirl marks, light scratches, oxidation, and haze.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">
                This stage may involve multiple correction levels, depending on the condition of the vehicle
              </h3>
              <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <li class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-neutral-700 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20 font-bold text-xs">1</div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Cutting stages to remove deeper defects</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-neutral-700 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20 font-bold text-xs">2</div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Refinement stages to restore gloss and clarity</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-neutral-700 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20 font-bold text-xs">3</div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Controlled polishing to enhance depth and reflection</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
              Every panel is inspected under proper lighting before and after correction, ensuring consistency, balance, and maximum visual impact.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed font-bold border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6 py-2">
              This is where the transformation becomes visible. The paint begins to return to life.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Day 3 Section */}
        <div class="pt-20 border-t-2 border-neutral-100 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start group">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-4 lg:sticky lg:top-48">
            <div class="text-xs font-black text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-2">Stage 03</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-4xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-neutral-950 leading-tight group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors duration-300">
              Day 3: <br class="hidden lg:block" />Protection & <br class="hidden lg:block" />Final Sealing
            </h2>
            <div class="w-12 h-1.5 bg-blue-600/30 group-hover:w-24 transition-all duration-500"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-800 font-extrabold leading-relaxed">
              Restoration without protection is temporary. The final stage ensures that the transformation is preserved.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
              Day three is focused on sealing and protecting every surface that has been restored.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4">This includes</h3>
              <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-6">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Final surface preparation and wipe-down</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Professional application of a 5-year ceramic coating</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Careful layering for durability, gloss, and hydrophobic performance</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Protection of exterior paintwork against UV damage, contamination, and environmental wear</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-neutral-700">
                  <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-blue-600/20">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-base font-bold leading-tight">Final interior finishing touches to ensure a complete presentation</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed font-bold border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6 py-2">
              The ceramic coating acts as a long-term shield—locking in gloss, enhancing depth, and making future maintenance significantly easier.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      {/* The Result Conclusion */}
      <div class="py-24 border-t border-neutral-100">
        <div class="bg-neutral-950 text-white p-12 md:p-24 rounded-3xl border border-blue-600/20 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <div class="absolute -right-24 -bottom-24 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="absolute -left-24 -top-24 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-600/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

          <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12 relative z-10">
            <div class="text-xs font-black text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">The Ultimate Transformation</div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">
              The Result
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                After three days of structured restoration, the vehicle is no longer simply cleaned or polished.
              </p>
              <p class="text-white font-extrabold border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6 text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight uppercase">
                It is reset.
              </p>
              <p class="font-bold text-white text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight uppercase">
                Restored in clarity. Refined in finish. Protected for the future.
              </p>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 font-light">
                Every surface reflects intention. Every detail carries precision. The vehicle leaves not just improved—but transformed into its highest possible version.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-8 border-t border-neutral-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-6">
              <p class="text-blue-500 text-base md:text-lg uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-black leading-normal">
                This is not detailing as a service. <br/><span class="text-white">It is detailing as a system.</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Action Buttons */}
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center pt-12">
        <button id="add-omega-from-process" class="px-12 py-6 bg-blue-600 text-white font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-neutral-900 transition-all text-sm rounded-xl shadow-xl shadow-blue-600/20 hover:shadow-neutral-900/20 cursor-pointer">
          Add The Omega Detail (R9000)
        </button>
        <a href="/pricing" class="px-12 py-6 border-2 border-neutral-200 text-neutral-900 font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:border-blue-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-all text-sm rounded-xl text-center">
          Back to Pricing
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />

  {/* Success Toast */}
  <div id="toast" class="fixed bottom-10 right-10 z-[100] translate-y-20 opacity-0 transition-all duration-500 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-10 py-5 font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-xs flex items-center gap-6 shadow-2xl border border-white/20 rounded-xl">
      <div class="p-2 bg-white/20 rounded-full">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
         <span class="text-[10px] opacity-70">Success</span>
         <span>Item Added to Cart</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    const btn = document.getElementById('add-omega-from-process');
    btn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const cart = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('omega-cart') || '[]');
      cart.push({ name: 'The Omega Detail (All Sizes)', price: 9000 });
      localStorage.setItem('omega-cart', JSON.stringify(cart));
      
      // Show toast
      const toast = document.getElementById('toast');
      toast?.classList.remove('translate-y-20', 'opacity-0');
      setTimeout(() => {
        toast?.classList.add('translate-y-20', 'opacity-0');
      }, 4000);
    });
  </script>

  <style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes slideUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .animate-fade-in {
      animation: fadeIn 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    }
    .animate-slide-up {
      animation: slideUp 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    }
    main { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
  </style>
</Layout>
